text: Villiam Nieminen (29 February 1888 - 13 April 1972) was a Finnish gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:1972 deaths Category:Finnish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Finland Category:Gymnasts at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tampere
